        <p>5 championship courses. Free quote in 24 hours. Groups of 4 to 200.</p>
        <a href="/request-a-quote/" class="bl-cta-btn btn-green-glow">Get a Free Quote →</a>
        <div class="bl-cta-links">
          <a href="/all-golf-courses/">Compare all 5 Graeagle courses →</a>
